					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"Her beauty is wasted on the Tachibana household, but at the same time she makes a surprisingly good match.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"这对橘家来说美得有点浪费，但同时也惊人地适合。",
