					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"So I’ve been bringing packed lunches to the student committee room every lunch.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"所以我才会像现在一样，在午休时间把便当送到学生会室来。",
