				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "Rei"},
					"“The vice president is already out wearing the Hamedori suit peddling them, and Mizuki disappeared running after the former governor Hitoura. That girl really has daddy issues...”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"“副会长去卖Hamedori的套装了、水姬则是追随着仁浦前县长不知道去了哪里⋯⋯毕竟那家伙是个不折不扣的大叔控⋯⋯”",
