					"在刚在的对话里，我的肌肉之眼早就看到会长会动不动卷到自己的披风。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"在剛在的對話裡，我的肌肉之眼早就看到會長會動不動捲到自己的披風。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00300",
		linknext = "0090_00302",
		line = 4344,
	},
	["0090_00302"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"It seems the head of the disciplinary committee and the commander have been looking after her at home, too.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"看样子在家里，风纪委员长跟中队长就是这样照顾着冷泉院的。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"看樣子在家裡，風紀委員長跟中隊長就是這樣照顧著冷泉院的。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00301",
		linknext = "0090_00303",
		line = 4354,
	},
	["0090_00303"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"When I ask, they tell me things are much the same as when they were at the FS dorm. But surely things have changed a lot since then.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"我问了一下，似乎她们在FS宿舍的时候也是这样的⋯⋯不过，她们的生活已经发生了巨变。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"我問了一下，似乎她們在FS宿舍的時候也是這樣的⋯⋯不過，她們的生活已經發生了巨變。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00302",
		linknext = "0090_00304",
		line = 4364,
	},
	["0090_00304"] = {
		{"fg", file="ikuko_01m_00001", file1="ikuko_01m_00101", file2="ikuko_01m_00205", path=":fg/ikuko_01m/", id=10, lv=10, head="ikuko_01m", ch_origin="郁子", ch="郁子10", mw="mw", sync=0, mode=3, x=595, y=-5},
		{"transitiontime", time=300},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			vo = {
				{"vo", file="ikuko2051", path=":vo/", ch="ikuko"},
			},
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"郁子", "Ikuko"},
					"“Who would’ve thought I would fall this far...?”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"“郁完全没有想过自己会沦落到这种地步呢。”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"「郁完全沒有想過自己會淪落到這種地步呢。」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00303",
		linknext = "0090_00305",
		line = 4379,
	},
	["0090_00305"] = {
		{"fg", file="rei_02m_00001", file1="rei_02m_00101", file2="rei_02m_00210", path=":fg/rei_02m/", id=9, lv=8, head="rei_02m", ch_origin="礼", ch="礼9", mw="mw", sync=0, mode=3, x=-605, y=-5},
		{"transitiontime", time=300},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			vo = {
				{"vo", file="rei2000", path=":vo/", ch="rei"},
			},
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "Rei"},
					"“It sucks... I’m doing all I can to put food on the table for my brothers...”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"“真是的⋯⋯光是养活弟弟们就够我累了⋯⋯”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "禮"},
					"「真是的⋯⋯光是養活弟弟們就夠我累了⋯⋯」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00304",
		linknext = "0090_00306",
		line = 4394,
	},
	["0090_00306"] = {
		{"fg", file="tohka_02m_00012", file1="tohka_02m_00101", file2="tohka_02m_00228", path=":fg/tohka_02m/", id=8, lv=9, head="tohka_02m", ch_origin="桐香", ch="桐香8", mw="mw", sync=0, mode=3, x=-5, y=-5},
		{"transitiontime", time=300},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			vo = {
				{"vo", file="tohka1772", path=":vo/", ch="touka"},
			},
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"桐香"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"桐香", "Touka"},
					"“Come on now. Don’t forget I was able get more scholarship money than you two. I help you out, remember.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"桐香"},
					"“不过你看，我的奖学金比他们两个都还要多喔，还可以靠这个对吧？”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"桐香"},
					"「不過你看，我的獎學金比他們兩個都還要多喔，還可以靠這個對吧？」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00305",
		linknext = "0090_00307",
		line = 4409,
	},
	["0090_00307"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"Apparently Reizeiin doles out some of her scholarship to the prez because of her dire situation, and it’s not an insignificant amount of money.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"家境最苛刻的风纪股长，现在正靠着冷泉院的奖学金──看样子是相当大的额度──过活着。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"家境最苛刻的風紀股長，現在正靠著冷泉院的獎學金──看樣子是相當大的額度──過活著。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00306",
		linknext = "0090_00308",
		line = 4419,
	},
	["0090_00308"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"That’s why the three of them can’t survive without each other.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"所以他们三个人才非得要一起生活。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"所以他們三個人才非得要一起生活。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00307",
		linknext = "0090_00309",
		line = 4429,
	},
	["0090_00309"] = {
		{"fg", file="ikuko_02m_00006", file1="ikuko_02m_00101", file2="ikuko_02m_00204", path=":fg/ikuko_02m/", id=10, lv=10, head="ikuko_02m", ch_origin="郁子", ch="郁子10", mw="mw", sync=0, mode=3, x=595, y=-5},
		{"transitiontime", time=300},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			vo = {
				{"vo", file="ikuko2052", path=":vo/", ch="ikuko"},
			},
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"郁子", "Ikuko"},
					"“But weren’t you the one who processed the FS scholarships, Touka? That’s why we couldn’t submit ours in time.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"“不过，说起来是因为桐香酱忙着帮我们两个以外的FS处理奖学金还有补助的手续，所以才来不及办我们自己的吧？”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"「不過，說起來是因為桐香醬忙著幫我們兩個以外的FS處理獎學金還有補助的手續，所以才來不及辦我們自己的吧？」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00308",
		linknext = "0090_00310",
		line = 4444,
	},
	["0090_00310"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"The collapse of the FS put its former members in a bit of a pinch.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"FS瓦解了，原本靠着奖学金生活的学生们似乎会连生活都有困难。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"FS瓦解了，原本靠著獎學金生活的學生們似乎會連生活都有困難。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00309",
		linknext = "0090_00311",
		line = 4454,
	},
	["0090_00311"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"Reizeiin got busy, finding alternative scholarships, handling documentation, and even traveling to other prefectures for meetings.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"那时，是冷泉院替所有人另觅奖学金、制作文书资料，到其他县市去斡旋，想办法解决的。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"那時，是冷泉院替所有人另覓獎學金、製作文書資料，到其他縣市去斡旋，想辦法解決的。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00310",
		linknext = "0090_00312",
		line = 4464,
	},
	["0090_00312"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"It must have been a massive amount of money, because the FS had more than 20 or 30 members.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"FS们的数量可不是只有区区二三十个人，而是个庞大的数量。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"FS們的數量可不是只有區區二三十個人，而是個龐大的數量。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00311",
		linknext = "0090_00313",
		line = 4474,
	},
	["0090_00313"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"They were able to save themselves from ruin by releasing almost all of it to other prefectures and sourcing allowances for students unable to leave the island.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"几乎所有的FS最后都去了其他县市，也为那些无法离岛的学生们找了各种补助，将他们堪堪从这场灭顶之灾给救了出来。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"幾乎所有的FS最後都去了其他縣市，也為那些無法離島的學生們找了各種補助，將他們堪堪從這場滅頂之災給救了出來。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00312",
		linknext = "0090_00314",
		line = 4484,
	},
	["0090_00314"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"But as a result of all their hard work, the top three weren’t able to process their own documentation in time.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"由于这些事几乎都是她一手包办的，所以身为最上层的三个人连手续的时间都来不及赶上。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"由於這些事幾乎都是她一手包辦的，所以身為最上層的三個人連手續的時間都來不及趕上。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00313",
		linknext = "0090_00315",
		line = 4494,
	},
	["0090_00315"] = {
		{"fg", file="ikuko_02m_00006", file1="ikuko_02m_00101", file2="ikuko_02m_00204", path=":fg/ikuko_02m/", id=10, lv=10, head="ikuko_02m", ch_origin="郁子", ch="郁子10", mw="mw", sync=0, mode=3, x=595, y=-5},
		{"transitiontime", time=300},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			vo = {
				{"vo", file="ikuko2053", path=":vo/", ch="ikuko"},
			},
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"郁子", "Ikuko"},
					"“But you’ve been having way more fun now that the pervert sex law is gone, huh, Touka?”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"“虽然是这样，不过自从变态条例被废除后，桐香酱看起来也更开心了喔？”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"「雖然是這樣，不過自從變態條例被廢除後，桐香醬看起來也更開心了喔？」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00314",
		linknext = "0090_00316",
		line = 4509,
	},
	["0090_00316"] = {
		{"fg", file="rei_01m_00001", file1="rei_01m_00102", file2="rei_01m_00219", path=":fg/rei_01m/", id=9, lv=8, head="rei_01m", ch_origin="礼", ch="礼9", mw="mw", sync=0, mode=3, x=-605, y=-5},
		{"fgact", ch="礼9", id=9, act="移動", x=200, y=0, time=800},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			vo = {
				{"vo", file="rei2001", path=":vo/", ch="rei"},
			},
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "Rei"},
					"“Hey, you don’t have to say it like that. Things have just gotten easier for her now that she’s dropped the stuffy title.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"“喂，别说这种挖苦的话⋯⋯是因为肩上的重担终于卸掉了一个所以才轻松了一点⋯⋯”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "禮"},
					"「喂，別說這種挖苦的話⋯⋯是因為肩上的重擔終於卸掉了一個所以才輕鬆了一點⋯⋯」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00315",
		linknext = "0090_00317",
		line = 4524,
	},
	["0090_00317"] = {
		{"se", id=0, loop=0, file="se_a098"},
		{"fg", file="rei_02m_00001", file1="rei_02m_00102", file2="rei_02m_00223", path=":fg/rei_02m/", id=9, lv=8, head="rei_02m", ch_origin="礼", ch="礼9", mw="mw", sync=0, mode=3, x=-405, y=-5},
		{"fgact", ch="礼9", id=9, act="移動", x=-200, y=0, time=300},
		{"fg", file="ikuko_02m_00006", file1="ikuko_02m_00101", file2="ikuko_02m_00203", path=":fg/ikuko_02m/", id=10, lv=10, head="ikuko_02m", ch_origin="郁子", ch="郁子10", mw="mw", sync=0, mode=3, x=595, y=-5},
		{"fgact", ch="郁子10", id=10, act="振動下", loop=1, size=12.5, time=150, ease="easeinout_sine"},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			vo = {
				{"vo", file="ikuko2054", path=":vo/", ch="ikuko"},
			},
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"郁子", "Ikuko"},
					"“Urgh, you’re always way too soft on Touka! I’ve been telling you this whole time!”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"“吼！所以我才说礼酱你平常太宠桐香酱了嘛！我之前不就这样说过了吗！？”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"「吼！所以我才說禮醬你平常太寵桐香醬了嘛！我之前不就這樣說過了嗎！？」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0090_00316",
		linknext = "0090_00318",
		line = 4543,
	},
	["0090_00318"] = {
		{"fg", file="rei_01m_00001", file1="rei_01m_00101", file2="rei_01m_00224", path=":fg/rei_01m/", id=9, lv=8, head="rei_01m", ch_origin="礼", ch="礼9", mw="mw", sync=0, mode=3, x=-605, y=-5},
